## Warm Up

WOD: 54
All levels:
Warm up by doing:  3 rounds of 10 push ups, 10 sit ups, 10 pull   ups and 10 air squats.
Run 1 mile OR row 2000m OR bike 10 miles

as quickly as possible.  Post your time to comments.

